Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.80,0:00:41.90,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}子供の頃の夢は
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.06,0:00:45.13,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}色褪せない落書きで
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.34,0:00:48.95,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}思うまま書き滑らせて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.95,0:00:53.92,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}描く未来へとつながる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.18,0:01:02.49,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}澄み渡る空
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.12,0:01:06.00,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}果てしないほど青く
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.07,0:01:10.02,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}無邪気な心に
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.24,0:01:13.62,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}充たされ魅かれてく
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.78,0:01:17.58,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}やがて自由に飛びまわれる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.58,0:01:20.62,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}翼を手に入れて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.15,0:01:25.12,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}無垢な瞳は求めてく
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.12,0:01:28.92,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}空の向こうへ　行きたいな
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.92,0:01:32.02,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}止め処ない願いから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.20,0:01:35.37,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}一つだけ叶うのなら
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.47,0:01:39.11,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}誰にも譲りたくはない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.18,0:01:43.11,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}夢を掴みたいと思うよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.12,0:01:46.32,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}子供の頃の夢は
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.56,0:01:49.59,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}色褪せない落書きで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.82,0:01:53.52,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}いつまでも描き続けられた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.52,0:01:58.62,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}願う未来へとつながる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.80,0:00:41.90,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}孩童時的那個夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.06,0:00:45.13,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}是永不退色的塗鴉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.34,0:00:48.95,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}隨心所欲地去描繪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.95,0:00:53.92,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}走向自己描繪的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.18,0:01:02.49,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}萬里無雲的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.12,0:01:06.00,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}無邊無際的蔚藍
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.07,0:01:10.02,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}純潔無瑕的心靈
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.24,0:01:13.62,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}充盈著無限魅力
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.78,0:01:17.58,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}終於能自由翱翔於天空
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.58,0:01:20.62,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}長出了美麗的羽翼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.15,0:01:25.12,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}無瑕的瞳孔在尋求
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.12,0:01:28.92,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}想去那天空的彼岸
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.92,0:01:32.02,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}在那無數的願望中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.20,0:01:35.37,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}若是只有一個能實現
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.47,0:01:39.11,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}我不願讓給任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.18,0:01:43.11,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}要緊緊抓住那夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.12,0:01:46.32,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}孩童時的那個夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.56,0:01:49.59,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}是永不退色的塗鴉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.82,0:01:53.52,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}永不停息地去描寫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.52,0:01:58.62,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}走向自己祈願的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.40,0:23:14.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,780)\fad(1000,8)\3a&00&\3c&0000A0&}戰禍
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.78,0:21:44.23,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}炎さえも凍てついた
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.73,0:21:50.89,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}孤独の中求む
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.89,0:21:59.55,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}魂から結びつき
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.77,0:22:07.58,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}私を恋い暖めて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.73,0:22:16.40,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}嗚呼　祈りの言葉がふるえ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.74,0:22:24.11,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}嗚呼　弱きいのちが消えても
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.82,0:22:31.98,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}くりかえす　輪廻の流れ辿り
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.09,0:22:40.60,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}終わらない世界の宿命を見つめてる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.66,0:22:48.10,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}くりかえし　詠われる者達よ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.11,0:22:56.24,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}守られてまどろむ宵
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.78,0:21:44.23,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}就算火焰都凍結
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.73,0:21:50.89,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}也在孤獨中尋求
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.89,0:21:59.55,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}請用靈魂連結我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.77,0:22:07.58,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}請用愛戀溫暖我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.73,0:22:16.40,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}嗚呼 那顫抖的祈願之聲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.74,0:22:24.11,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}嗚呼 那脆弱的生命消逝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.82,0:22:31.98,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}追溯那不斷交替的輪迴之流
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.09,0:22:40.60,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}凝望那永不終結的世界的宿命
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.66,0:22:48.10,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}不斷輪迴的 那些傳頌之物
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.11,0:22:56.24,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}被守護著安眠的夜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.06,0:00:11.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉庫夏
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.44,0:00:16.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,東霞閣下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.54,0:00:18.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您沒事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.18,0:00:20.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奧利卡坎殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.23,0:00:23.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都怪在下不夠成熟
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.00,0:00:24.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.94,0:00:26.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是東霞閣下的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.87,0:00:28.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是他們卑鄙而已
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.84,0:00:33.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以艾文庫魯加的名義擔保
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.46,0:00:35.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次是不會讓他們逃掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.80,0:02:10.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.84,0:02:11.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說過了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.09,0:02:12.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.76,0:02:15.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是敵人裡面有艾文庫魯加族的人這事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.03,0:02:18.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來那是真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.66,0:02:23.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼艾文庫魯加幫藩族的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.78,0:02:24.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.90,0:02:26.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾文庫魯加是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.08,0:02:29.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾文庫魯加就是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.13,0:02:33.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫助世間好人 斬惡除奸的高貴…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.24,0:02:35.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那白皇大人是壞人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.50,0:02:41.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那之後
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.74,0:02:45.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奧利卡坎的騎兵隊為了不讓我們追蹤而分散開來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.39,0:02:49.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,潛入黑夜消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.66,0:02:56.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在猜到了幾處他們可能匯合的地點 正派人調查
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.56,0:02:57.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,民眾的情況如何
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.09,0:03:04.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用介意 說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.68,0:03:09.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都在動搖著
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.11,0:03:12.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.12,0:03:13.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也對
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.07,0:03:16.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.04,0:03:17.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.06,0:03:18.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.89,0:03:23.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖上也請去休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.63,0:03:27.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為萬事都做好準備
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.36,0:03:29.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是領導者的職責
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.38,0:03:36.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也對
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.37,0:03:41.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不錯的味道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.06,0:03:42.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡露拉小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.41,0:03:44.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.74,0:03:46.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是哈克奧羅的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.44,0:03:51.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以的話卡露拉小姐也一起享用好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.40,0:03:53.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.39,0:03:57.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然機會難得
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.91,0:03:59.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妨礙你們也不好的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.82,0:04:03.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是個好機會
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.43,0:04:04.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盡情撒嬌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.82,0:04:05.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.67,0:04:08.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許情況應該相反呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.04,0:04:10.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那位大人煩惱的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.17,0:04:14.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓他撒一下嬌也是女人的職責呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.93,0:04:17.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我要走了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.43,0:04:34.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就喝這些吧 也應該去休息了…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.10,0:04:35.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.50,0:04:37.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我再喝一會兒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.44,0:04:48.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天都這樣子 我作為藥師不可以袖手旁觀了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.24,0:04:51.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你擔心我的身體嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.06,0:04:53.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.51,0:04:57.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天艾露露都因為同樣的事批評我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.02,0:05:00.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都要怪哈克奧羅不去休息
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.18,0:05:01.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝那麼多酒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.58,0:05:07.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母親在的話也會說同樣的話吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.03,0:05:09.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.62,0:05:10.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親在的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.58,0:05:13.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是否會責罵我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.97,0:05:16.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈克奧羅
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.19,0:05:19.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記不起父親母親的我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.04,0:05:22.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有自身記憶的我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.99,0:05:24.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彷彿把你當成了母親
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.95,0:05:31.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈克奧羅
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.59,0:05:37.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為連自己是誰也不知道而感到不安
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.28,0:05:39.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是很滑稽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.55,0:05:44.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.16,0:05:46.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.95,0:06:01.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈克奧羅不管是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.34,0:06:03.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.77,0:06:07.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都沒關係…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.70,0:06:10.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我來說 哈克奧羅
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.61,0:06:13.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是哈克奧羅
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.18,0:06:16.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.27,0:06:28.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈克奧羅
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.97,0:06:35.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不害怕我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.16,0:06:44.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.51,0:06:46.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,退下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.85,0:07:07.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是絕對不會害怕哈克奧羅的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.97,0:07:10.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.76,0:07:11.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.31,0:07:16.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.60,0:07:20.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克羅
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.53,0:07:21.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,見到兄長嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.13,0:07:22.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.32,0:07:24.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不在房間裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.77,0:07:28.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這麼重要的時候去哪裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.64,0:07:31.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖上也有自己的想法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.73,0:07:32.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然那也對
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.30,0:07:36.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但庫查·凱查隨時都有可能攻過來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.55,0:07:40.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾露露大人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.69,0:07:41.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.26,0:07:44.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要拿些傷藥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.93,0:07:46.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在找艾露露大人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.67,0:07:55.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傷藥的話我給你們拿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.43,0:08:04.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 不要跑得太遠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.01,0:08:08.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈克奧羅
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.29,0:08:12.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你今天陪我們出來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.06,0:08:13.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒不如說
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.72,0:08:15.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我硬把你拉出來的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.93,0:08:17.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾露露
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.09,0:08:18.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.83,0:08:21.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也對呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.55,0:08:24.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都在擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.52,0:08:29.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈克奧羅是大家的白皇
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.25,0:08:32.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對你…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.45,0:08:36.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是偶爾也是要休息的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.32,0:08:42.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.46,0:08:47.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要這樣支持我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.31,0:08:53.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我總是給你增加痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.71,0:08:55.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.44,0:08:57.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.94,0:09:03.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還記得嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.62,0:09:07.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈克奧羅說過我們是一家人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.09,0:09:13.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不可以成為理由嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.74,0:09:18.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有那麼深厚的意義的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.01,0:09:22.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 只是 這個 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.73,0:09:24.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.00,0:09:31.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好開心哦 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.88,0:09:37.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好開心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.31,0:09:48.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 也對
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.18,0:09:53.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.15,0:10:05.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 別這樣 穆庫魯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.79,0:10:50.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵襲 敵襲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.00,0:10:52.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.06,0:10:54.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.92,0:11:06.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兄長
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.55,0:11:15.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出陣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.01,0:11:20.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白皇大人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.19,0:11:22.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個人數沒問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.77,0:11:24.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會不會太草率
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.60,0:11:25.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人的速度很快
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.88,0:11:27.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是帶上疲敝的士兵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.67,0:11:29.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只會使我們的損失更慘重
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.71,0:11:31.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然這也有道理
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.72,0:11:38.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正不用擔心就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.30,0:11:40.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穆庫魯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.47,0:11:41.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,守門要靠你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.25,0:11:45.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.80,0:11:46.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.97,0:11:55.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是很重要的戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.25,0:11:56.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要掉以輕心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.05,0:12:00.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是你自己 總是一股蠻勁可不好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.41,0:12:05.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.32,0:12:13.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒到吃飯時間
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.21,0:12:18.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常遺憾
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.87,0:12:22.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是邊境的藩族沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.65,0:12:25.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白皇大人是很賢明的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.42,0:12:28.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那位大人自己站在前面
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.54,0:12:32.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給大家引路
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.20,0:12:35.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神結
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.32,0:12:38.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.00,0:12:42.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.60,0:12:45.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…要幫助叔叔的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.61,0:12:46.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.82,0:12:48.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.57,0:12:52.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大神教會的使者怎麼可以自願參與戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.37,0:12:53.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.66,0:12:56.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.65,0:12:57.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神結
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.91,0:12:59.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒙特說得沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.19,0:13:01.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.32,0:13:07.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.26,0:13:08.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔不會有事的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.95,0:13:11.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然這是很艱辛的戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.34,0:13:17.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但現在這個國家必須經歷這道試煉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.78,0:13:20.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.15,0:13:24.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,願「解放者」保佑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.69,0:13:37.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,派去追蹤的士兵
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.19,0:13:38.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一人也沒有回來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.75,0:13:40.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.29,0:13:41.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.09,0:13:43.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.53,0:13:44.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人很勇猛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.92,0:13:46.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輕敵的話會被壓垮
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.21,0:13:48.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.92,0:13:50.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的我不討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.76,0:13:51.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兄長
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.27,0:13:53.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.44,0:14:01.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作個了結吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.84,0:14:18.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正合我意
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.95,0:14:20.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我殺
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.35,0:14:33.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不玩小花樣 這讓人刮目相看了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.32,0:14:35.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉庫夏
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.40,0:14:37.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉庫夏在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.05,0:14:43.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想死的話就讓出路來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.00,0:15:00.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然是艾文庫魯加的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.93,0:15:04.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼作為對手沒有任何不足
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.63,0:15:20.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉庫夏
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.66,0:15:22.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉庫夏
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.83,0:15:28.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.77,0:15:29.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想逃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.76,0:15:30.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奧利卡坎殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.06,0:15:35.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要孤身追敵
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.64,0:15:36.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奧利卡坎殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.97,0:15:44.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克羅
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.66,0:15:45.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別讓她追
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.46,0:16:01.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.92,0:16:03.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡禁止通行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.78,0:16:06.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不這樣做的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.64,0:16:08.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就沒辦法絆住你了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.47,0:16:25.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卑鄙小人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.31,0:16:28.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說得還真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.66,0:16:37.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別以為會讓你死得痛快
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.71,0:16:46.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.78,0:16:47.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停下來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.66,0:16:58.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.59,0:17:02.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,決戰要留到下次了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.61,0:17:09.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你死定了 拉庫夏
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.70,0:17:12.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連害怕之心也早已丟失了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.15,0:17:15.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引你來這裡是策略之一
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.89,0:17:17.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這是求饒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.77,0:17:19.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會聽的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.47,0:17:23.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不這樣做的話就不能和你交談了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.89,0:17:26.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別小看我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.19,0:17:30.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在我再問一次
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.83,0:17:35.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的知道我的過去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.22,0:17:37.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還用問嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.53,0:17:51.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉庫夏
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.94,0:17:52.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到此為止了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.96,0:18:03.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.72,0:18:04.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.47,0:18:07.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把妻子殺死
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.20,0:18:09.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,子女也殺死
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.52,0:18:12.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奪走我的一切 使我無顏面世
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.72,0:18:15.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心情非常不錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.62,0:18:16.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.64,0:18:17.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.95,0:18:19.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.76,0:18:21.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像殺我妹妹那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.53,0:18:23.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用你的手來殺我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.99,0:18:24.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉庫夏
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.66,0:18:28.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.13,0:18:31.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事已至此還想裝傻嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.86,0:18:33.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是哈克奧羅
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.96,0:18:35.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是什麼拉庫夏
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.79,0:18:36.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一派胡言
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.56,0:18:39.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是記憶沒有了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.79,0:18:41.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的罪也不會消失的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.72,0:18:43.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罪？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.21,0:18:45.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.58,0:18:49.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那染滿鮮血的雙手就是最好的證據
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.18,0:18:53.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.85,0:19:13.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.32,0:19:17.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是這種程度的東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.02,0:19:19.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.80,0:19:21.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你究竟是什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.81,0:19:25.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.14,0:19:28.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別過來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.49,0:19:28.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.53,0:19:30.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.20,0:19:33.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看到了我的什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.69,0:19:48.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙的使命到此為止了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.52,0:19:53.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部都是為了你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.65,0:19:55.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了煽動你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.11,0:19:57.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而利用了那個人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.24,0:20:03.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要做這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.10,0:20:05.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.20,0:20:06.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這種憤怒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.57,0:20:09.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本王想看看沉睡於你體內的獸物
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.98,0:20:14.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憤怒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.94,0:20:15.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怨恨吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.90,0:20:16.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憎惡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.23,0:20:19.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那正是人的力量之源
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.64,0:20:22.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令本王快樂的源泉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.38,0:20:27.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,豈有此理
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.64,0:20:29.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奧利卡坎殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.53,0:20:34.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下做了無可挽回的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.35,0:20:48.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現實就是快樂的戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.27,0:21:06.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈克奧羅
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.59,0:21:12.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.39,0:21:14.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來


